content: He can't get to the polls easily.
Are you still on the call with him?
no but i have his info still up. he was older and wasn't able to write down mail in ballot info
We can't reach out to anyone directly. The best thing to do is to give them the WI voter hotline number at 608-336-3232
Ah ok.  He wasn't able to take down the number. Hope he's able to vote. I told him to make sure his daughter knew to get him a new ballot if needed.
That's great! They're publicizing the number and hopefully she can find the WI tracker info too. Great suggestion.
